trans-unit.source: Specifies how a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel"></xref> will gain additional rows or columns after its existing cells are full.
trans-unit.target: Angir hvordan en <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel"> </xref> vil få flere rader eller kolonner når de eksisterende cellene er full.

trans-unit.source: If all the cells in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel> are filled and the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel.GrowStyle%2A> property is set to FixedSize, an attempt to add another control will throw an exception.
trans-unit.target: Hvis alle cellene i de <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel>fylles og <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel.GrowStyle%2A>er satt til FixedSize, vil et forsøk på å legge til en annen kontroll Iverksett et unntak.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel.GrowStyle%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel"></xref> gains additional columns after it is full.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel"> </xref> får tilleggskolonner når den er full.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel"></xref> gains additional rows after it is full.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel"> </xref> får flere rader når den er full.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel"></xref> does not allow additional rows or columns after it is full.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel"> </xref> tillater ikke flere rader eller kolonner når den er full.
